主要翻译
 
melancholy n (emotion: sadness)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 忧伤 yōu shāng  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 哀伤 yōu shāng，āi shāng 
 -- He was overcome with melancholy after his wife's death.
 
melancholy adj (person: sad)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 忧伤的，哀伤的 yōu shāng de ，āi shāng de TC Traditional Chinese 哀傷的  (人)
 -- You look so melancholy - what's wrong?
 
melancholy adj (atmosphere: gloomy)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 忧伤的，令人哀伤的 yōu shāng de ，lìng rén āi shāng de  (氛围)
 -- She lives alone in a melancholy old mansion.

